      • GCS_DELETE_BATCH_SIZE_DEFAULT

        public static final int GCS_DELETE_BATCH_SIZE_DEFAULT
        Max possible batch size for deletion. Currently, a max of 100 keys is advised, so we default to a number below that. https://cloud.google.com/storage/docs/batch
